Alas Del Kealoha is our newest home build, luxurious large private gated house located in the heart of Volcano Village. This beautiful getaway home is a well illuminated 3 bedroom / 2 bath one-story pine house.
This 3 bedroom / 2 bath bedroom large home is perfect for large families, friends traveling together, a special anniversary, or as a writer or artist`s retreat.

Guests can take pleasure in it`s private hot tub on the wide lanai-patio after playing a ping pong game and preparing a big barbecue on the grill. For guests relaxation, the discovery of a perfect temperature hot tub to soak after an adventurous day at the Volcanoes National Park will fulfill all expectations and dreams. For guests comfort, robes to get out of the hot tub, and big basket for outside hot tub towels are at one`s disposal.
Internet, cable and a 55" flat screen home theater that has unlimited Netflix, Pandora, Facebook, and other cool features. Movies and Hawaiian books are also available.
Full kitchen, microwave, toaster, blender, coffee maker. BBQ grill, wood fireplace, hammocks, laundry facilities washing/dryer machines.
Enjoy natural beauty and incredible privacy. Step out your door and into a quiet time and place. Stroll down the canopied lanes located less than a half-mile from the heart of the village or take in some of the many sights of the island easily accessible from here.
Welcome to Alas del Kealoha Vacation Rental! By renting one of the newest and most comfortable houses in Volcano Village, you will also be part of the great adventure of discovering one of the last rain forest in the world.
